{
    "text": "What's up at Harvard?",
    "created": "Thu, 01 Feb 2024 22:10:59 GMT",
    "type": "outline",
    "description": "In my two years at Harvard in 00s, I never saw or experienced antisemetism there.",
    "metaImage": "https://imgs.scripting.com/2024/02/01/catsHeaderImage.png",
    "subs": [
        {
            "text": "I wrote this note to Chris Lydon re the <a href=\"https://radioopensource.org/the-humbling-of-harvard/\">latest episode</a> of his podcast. ",
            "created": "Thu, 01 Feb 2024 22:11:08 GMT",
            "subs": [
                {
                    "text": "Chris,",
                    "created": "Thu, 01 Feb 2024 22:11:25 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "I'm listening to your latest <a href=\"https://radioopensource.org/the-humbling-of-harvard/\">podcast about Harvard</a>, and totally appreciate this. ",
                    "created": "Thu, 01 Feb 2024 22:13:15 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "In my two years at Harvard in the 00s, I never:",
                    "subs": [
                        {
                            "text": "1. Experienced antisemitism.",
                            "created": "Thu, 01 Feb 2024 22:13:23 GMT",
                            "flInCalendar": true
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "2. Saw antisemitism.",
                            "flInCalendar": true
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "3. Even thought about the <i>possibility</i> of antisemitism.",
                            "created": "Thu, 01 Feb 2024 22:13:24 GMT",
                            "flInCalendar": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "On the Harvard campus.",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "That said, antisemitism is everywhere, even inside me, a man whose grandparents were Jews who fled for their lives with their children from the Holocaust before and during WWII. I am a product of that, in ways I didn't even realize until my parents were gone. It's everywhere, all around, inside myself, inside everyone, and the best we can hope for imho is that it will stay hidden. ",
                    "created": "Thu, 01 Feb 2024 22:13:55 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "Ask me about what happened in the NBA with <a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=site%3Ascripting.com+kyrie\">Kyrie Irving</a>, and how, by their silence, the players and coaches showed how huge and deep the problem is.",
                    "created": "Thu, 01 Feb 2024 22:14:48 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "To see the Repubs monetize this for political gain is par for the course. To see Harvard buckle under that, is as weak and the people who made that decision imho should resign in disgrace. ",
                    "created": "Thu, 01 Feb 2024 22:20:49 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "Thanks for your continued and unique excellence. ",
                    "created": "Thu, 01 Feb 2024 22:15:09 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "Dave",
                    "created": "Thu, 01 Feb 2024 22:15:10 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                }
            ],
            "flInCalendar": true
        }
    ],
    "flInCalendar": true
}